<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idfe8a0e3d-9d45-11f0-a0db-bff75580f504" identifier="/us/usc/t24/s17"><num value="17">§ 17.</num><heading> Government of Naval Asylum</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The asylum for disabled and decrepit Navy officers, seamen, and marines shall be governed in accordance with the rules and regulations prescribed by the Secretary of the Navy.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idfe8a0e3e-9d45-11f0-a0db-bff75580f504">(R.S. § 4811.)</sourceCredit>
